Azure Space represents an exciting future, where possibilities of space are combined with the power of the cloud. By extending Azure capabilities beyond the confines of earth, we're enabling organizations to connect to the cloud from anywhere, analyze and disseminate space data, and build and test in the cloud from space.

Now that you've completed this module and understand the current state of the space industry and some of the capabilities of the Azure Space portfolio, you can extend your knowledge with deeper dives into each of the products.

